{"type": "article", "id": 3465, "title": "Wood Melbourne 卫浴产品", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-12T07:23:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232833l0XBVQRcj8t4pmGP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自墨尔本的设计工作室 Wood Melbourne 日前推出了一淘卫浴系列产品，包括了水龙头、浴池出水口装置、水槽以及淋浴花洒等卫浴配件，皆由混凝土、木材与铬合金 3 种材质制作而成，设计团队专注于呈现原材料的纯粹性，简单的线条透出力量，显出原始自然的味道。这一系列的所有产品全部是由创始人 Oliver Maclatchy 的手工作坊手工完成，在保证了产品的工艺水平与质量的同时，又使得每一款产品呈现出独一无二的个性美感。定价 242－660 美元不等，<a href=\"http://woodmelbourne.com/collections/all\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232831Qk29VcyUainpHYMx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232831tqwdKITiBgz8PlW4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232832ShBrenlQvG6oXuZz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232832DszdJjfGEwhnIr03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232833SVLQmObaX6wGR4Nc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}